{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_01_02",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 2話 先輩のサポート",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日は星見市主催の野外イベント当日）\n（サニーピースも参加して、出番を待っていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Today’s the day of the outdoor event staged by Hoshimi City.)\n(Sunny Peace is taking part too‚ and waiting for their turn to come.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.563157834112644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.933333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "よいしょっと……さすがにこの量のペットボトルは\n重いなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh boy. I think I’m trying to carry too many\nbottles at once here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.466666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.133333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　どうしたの\nこんな所で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey. What’s up?\nWhat are you doing here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.133333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それはこっちのセリフです\nいつの間にかいなくなってて、驚きましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I should be the one asking you that.\nYou vanished‚ so I came looking for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　{user}君\nもしかして気付いてなかった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? {user}!\nYou didn’t see my text?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.066666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "挨拶回りで忙しそうにしてたから\nスマホに連絡入れといたんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You looked busy going around and greeting everyone‚\nso I sent a text to your phone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.666666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "しょうがないなぁ……\nでもまあ、私も心配させて、ごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Jeez…\nWell‚ sorry for making you worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、スポーツドリンクを買いに\nそこの自販機に寄ってたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I came to the vending machines\nto get some sports drinks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "今日はなんだか暑くなりそうでしょ？\n水分補給しないと、倒れちゃうから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s pretty hot today.\nWe need to keep hydrated so no one collapses.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.13333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "すみません！　そうでしたか……でも随分な数ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry! You’re right… but that’s a lot of bottles.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "一人二本だし、そうでもないわよ？\nそれに、多いに越したことはないじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Two bottles per girl. That’s all.\nYou can’t be too hydrated.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……ちなみにいくらでした？\n俺が支払います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How much did you spend?\nI’ll pay you back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "え？　いい、いい。大丈夫\n私が勝手に買ったんだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? No‚ no need. It’s fine.\nI was the one who decided to buy them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに所属アイドルに支払わせる訳には……\nそれに俺が運びますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t have an idol from my office paying for her own drinks.\nLet me carry them for you as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そう？　それじゃあ……ありがとう\nでも、本当に気にしないでいいからね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you insist‚ okay. Thanks.\nBut you really don’t have to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "こういうの、私の癖っていうか……\nしてあげないと落ち着かない性分、ってだけだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s just a habit of mine.\nI have to do things for people. Feel useful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……遙子さんは、やっぱり頼もしいですね\nみんなの先輩として、心強いですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re so reliable‚ Haruko-san.\nYou’re a reliable senpai to everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ、伊達にみんなより長くアイドルしてないし\nまあ……鳴かず飛ばずではあったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been an idol for a long time.\nI’ve picked up a few things along the way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、見てきたものも聞いてきたことも\nみんなより沢山あるのは事実だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There have been ups and downs‚ sure‚\nand I have got more experience than the others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "サポートしようって思っちゃうのよ\n先輩がしっかりしてないと、ね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That makes me want to support them.\nI have to set an example‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。本当に助かってます\nあっ、そろそろ楽屋に戻りましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And you’re doing a great job. Thank you so much.\nAh‚ we’d better get back to the waiting room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "そうだった！\n着替えとメイクもまだだったもんね。急ごっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!\nI still need to change and get my makeup done. Come on!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ……\n飲み物、喜んでくれたみたいでよかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe….\nEveryone seems to have appreciated the drinks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.23333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君も\n運んでくれてありがとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}.\nThanks for carrying them for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.76666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "元々は俺の仕事でしたし……ただ、良かったんですか？\n飲み物を準備したの遙子さんだって内緒にして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All part of the job. But are you sure\nyou want to keep it a secret that you prepared them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、いいのいいの。気にしないで\n言わなくていいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha. Sure I am. Don’t worry about it.\nNo need to tell them anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "だって、私が準備したって分かると\nみんな私を先輩だって意識し過ぎないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If they find out I got the drinks‚\nI’m worried they’ll start seeing me too much as their senpai.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "さっき、自分は先輩だからーとか言っちゃったし\n矛盾してるかもって気はするんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know I just talked about being their senpai‚\nso I guess this is a bit contradictory…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "みんなと一緒の時は、対等でいたいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but when we’re together‚ I want us to all be equals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（確かにサニピには年齢差の隔たりは感じないな）\n（対等であろうと努める遙子さんが大きな理由か）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She makes a good point. I don’t feel the age gaps in Sunny Peace‚)\n(and Haruko-san working hard to keep them all equal plays a big part in that.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
